Text: The installer says that this is version 1.0 - I have no idea if there are any more versions. It also has some shady looking "BONUS" app included which by the readme claims to teach you how to cheat on poker. I just deleted it.
In any case, I had no luck with this. The pics are the right size (2-3MB), but just can not display. Hundreds like that on the hard drive. Well, the search continues.

Works OK for me.
The program converts the original JPG to a very large BMP-file but that's no problem
